caption: Classical statue of a man with a horse on the West side of the bridge near the Eiffel Tower. This particular offering has them both in the nude with little to cover their modesty. A wonderful joining of two muscular beings.
It was an amazing experience, beautiful places to see a lot to do

This area, if possible, across Avenue Jacques Chirac, seems to be the de facto main entrance to the Eiffel Tower. This seems to be the best view of the tower without any obstructions. Let's aim here first.
Very good restaurant, the service is great
